</tr>
<tr>
<td style="padding:0 0.1em 0.4em;padding-top:0.15em;">
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Administrators" title="Wikipedia:Administrators">Administrators</a></li>
<li><a class="mw-selflink selflink">Banning policy</a></li>
